snippet.textDisplay: Being quite broke the only thing I can do is to put this video as top link on my own small website. We should spread the word about this channel, everywhere, anywhere and to anywhom. These informations need to get out to the people. I live in both Western Germany and on Mallorca, and there are still many, many people around me who are misinformed about this virus and viruses in general. Good health to you, Vincent Racaniello, hope for the best
